node.text:
More love. That’s Sashagai’s personal motto when it comes to life, her growing fashion business, and her biggest inspiration – you!  In this special video edition of SHEIN Stories, we’re continuing the celebration of our latest SHEIN X May Collection (say yes to body positivity!) by chatting with the creator behind Flaws of Couture, her fashion identity, and a behind-the-scenes look at her personal style.
🔗 http://shein.top/sg3un0g
#SHEINX

node.text:
🌏 SHEIN Cares For Animals 🌏

'Your Passion + Your Action = A Beautiful World for Animals.'
Let's join together to keep our animals protected!

Explore the magic of the animal kingdom, help support the incredible creatures around us! Which animals are in the pics?

🌈ENTER:⁠
🐯 Follow @sheinofficial & like this post.
🦓 Comment below: Which animals are in the pics?
🐼 Tag your besties!

P.S. 1 comment = 1 entry. Unlimited entries! allowed but no repeats!

Prizes:⁠
𝟭 𝙇𝙪𝙘𝙠𝙮 𝙒𝙞𝙣𝙣𝙚𝙧 -- $𝟭,𝟬𝟬𝟬 𝙎𝙃𝙀𝙄𝙉 𝙂𝙞𝙛𝙩 𝘾𝙤𝙙𝙚𝙨
𝟮𝟬 𝙒𝙞𝙣𝙣𝙚𝙧𝙨 𝙬𝙞𝙡𝙡 𝙚𝙖𝙘𝙝 𝙬𝙞𝙣 - 𝟭𝟬𝟬 𝙎𝙃𝙀𝙄𝙉 𝙂𝙞𝙛𝙩 𝘾𝙤𝙙𝙚𝙨
Winners will be announced on 7/28 in our story!
Stay tuned on our following #SHEINcares events on 7/29.

👉 Please Note:⁣⁠
1. Your accounts need to be public so that we can see your entries.⁣⁠
2. The gift code needs to have an email address registered to a SHEIN account. Multiple winners with the same address would be treated as one winner with one gift code.⁠
3. SHEIN reserves the right to final interpretation.
